<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Travel information</h3>
    Follow the signs from the town centre. Please look at the <a href="http://uk.multimap.com/p/browse.cgi?pc=ta15da" target="blank">multimap website</a>For information on bus, please click on link. <a href="http://www.somerset.nhs.uk/services/hospitals/musgrove/bustimes.html"> Click here! </a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>The site has a multi storey car park and delays through a lack of car parking are a thing of the past.  The car parks operate a pay on foot system.  The first 20 minutes is free and charges then range from £1 for up to an hour to £6.50 for between 4 and 24 hours.</p>
