<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Visiting information</h3>
<p>All wards allow visiting, usually between 10am and 9pm (this includes weekends and bank holidays); two visitors per patient are allowed in each session. To find out more about visiting times for specific wards.<br/>There may be circumstances where relatives wish to stay with patients outside of normal visiting times, for example when a patient is very ill, or if they are a carer. Please do not hesitate to discuss requests of this type with our ward staff.<br/>Please note that visitors may be asked to leave temporarily while a healthcare professional needs to carry out a consultation or procedure.<br/><br/>Do not visit if you have an infection, or have had an infection in the last two days.</p>
